videos.description: Silas Melson finds Killian Tillie cutting to the basket for the alley-oop  jam.
videos.headline: Gonzaga's Tillie throws down poster dunk

videos.description: Josh Perkins dribbles down court and pulls up for the transition three-pointer.
videos.headline: Gonzaga's Perkins hits from deep

videos.description: TJ Haws drives, shows the ball and makes the layup in traffic.
videos.headline: BYU's Haws makes a sweet move for the bucket

videos.description: TJ Haws drives and Eurosteps through traffic for the reverse layup.
videos.headline: Cougars' Haws is creative around the basket

videos.description: Johnathan Williams makes a nice jab-step then drives to the basket for the go-ahead bucket.
videos.headline: Bulldogs' Williams gets the clutch bucket

videos.description: Rui Hachimura grabs the loose ball, picks the ball up and dribbles again, committing a double-dribble that isn't called.
videos.headline: Gonzaga wins but not without a controversial call
